{"tid":1567238,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳] 警方失當行為列表 (List of HK Police Misconducts)","createTime":"2019-09-14T03:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T08:11:50.000Z","uid":278417,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"179954165c18f45a422fc83be38889dce679c048","tid":1567238,"uid":278417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>列表中是較為明顯，有網絡錄像佐證的警方失當行為事件</strong>。不少可能牽涉警員刑事行為（如朱經緯案），希望當事人考慮接觸律師（如透過612、星火、民陣等）跟進舉報/索償，否則只會讓懷疑涉事警員置身事外，亦籍此希望讓外國人瞭解香港警方失當行為情況。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>On the list are those more obvious Hong Kong Police misconduct incidents which are evident from video clips available on the Internet</strong>.  Many incidents might involve criminal conducts on the police officers' part (like the Chu Jing Wei case).  Hopefully the victims would consider contacting lawyers (such as through 612 Fund, Spark Alliance, Civil Human Rights Front) to follow-up on making reports/claims, otherwise culpable officers might escape justice.  Also hope this list could help foreigners to gain a better understanding of the situation in Hong Kong concerning police's misconducts.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>附有錄像連結的PDF列表檔案 (List with hyper link to video clips in PDF format)</strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lR0Xzh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lR0Xzh&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ70p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=17f0db54\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lR0Xzh</a><br />\n<br />\n列表圖片 Images of the List:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRZeTHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRZeTHm.jpg&h=7777fcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvPuHAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvPuHAL.jpg&h=98fd613c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TffxFnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTffxFnt.jpg&h=699e3d38&s={SIZE}\" />